  <brief_title>A Open Study to Evaluate the Performance of Dressing on Subject With High Risk of Skin Breakdown</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Centre, Post CE Mark, Open Study to Evaluate the Performance of Thin Self-adherent Dressing Coated With a Soft Silicone Layer on Subjects With a High Risk of Skin Breakdown</official_title>
