    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Provision of written informed consent

          -  Braden total score ≤ 12 at enrolment

          -  Male or female, ≥ 18 at enrolment

          -  No skin- breakdown

          -  Subject or family member is able to understand and comply with the requirements of the
             study, judged by the investigator

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Risk area dosen´t fit the dressing size

          -  Documented skin disease

          -  Kown allergy to any of the components in the dressing

          -  Previous enroled in present study

          -  Subject included in other ongoing clinical investigation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
